                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Pookie is a wild pet, bit tuned down now but still quite deadly to someone like me (and still kicks serious butt against other mobs).  
<br />

<br />
When my friends and I make a Vxed group, I insist on a snarer, it has saved me many times. We usually hunt at the disk near zone-in, so I park him away from me and it gives me plenty of time to catch pookie when charm breaks. (though pet guard here seems broken there, hardly ever paths back to where I park him)
<br />

<br />
I've hasted him for boss mobs at first but now I shy away from it. I do give pookie mage gear every time though, that is plenty to beef him up for some slaughtering.  <img src="images/smiles/boxer.gif" alt="boxer.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Yaden Samsara of TP
