                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Avoid running into respawn by:
<br />

<br />
Tipt:  Moving faster.  Sounds silly, I know, but that's what you have to do.  Move up to each mob as you fight, that way always leaving yourself plenty of running room.  Keep spell haste up on yourself (Boon of Reverence), and ALWAYS have levitate and SoW.  Use the hillsides to create more room.
<br />

<br />
Vxed:  You have to kill 100 mobs before you can hail the flag mob, so until you get close to that, just stay at the entrance.  No respawn to run into.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Eleandra
<br />
<a href="http://www.precisionstrike.net" target="_blank">www.precisionstrike.net</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
