                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I prefer root instead of mez for hungry pookas
<br />
- due to dots that are sometimes on the pet
<br />

<br />
root also allows you to have an "Active pet"
<br />
(pull mob to rooted pet, til root wears off)
<br />

<br />

<br />
only downside is that cleric/pally may break the root with a DD stun
<br />
