                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you're having problems with respawn, then I'd definately recommend giving your pet a pair of weapons.  You should tear thru the mobs fast enough to easily stay ahead of respawn.
<br />

<br />
Alternatively, you could stop at a few key points, and wait for respawn, clear it, and then continue on.   I rarely have the patience to do this, so I usually just speed up the group.
<br />

<br />
Another thing I'd suggest, is using Hynids instead of pookas.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=378985" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Tashim</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.botsguild.org/" target="_blank" class="postlink">Brotherhood of the Spider</a>, <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency" target="_blank" class="postlink">The Rathe</a>
