                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Stonemites are the things you need to look out for in terms of dotting the pet - dot lasts 15 mins and I have yet to be able to get it cured.
<br />

<br />
Chaos Claws or the Ukun snare don't last very long, and both can be cured.
<br />

<br />
Stonemites = bad for pets (let your tank take the hits, put your pet behind them)</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
