                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just to point out the obvious:
<br />

<br />
bsts have no MR adjusts, although their casting time is fantastic.  The best combo is a bst AND enchanter, for 2 slows (to catch aggro) with a tash inbetween, all in less casting time that one enchanter slow.  This beats shaman/mage for malo, which is resistable.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
