                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">WoM and Rune is my friend and with the extended mez aa there is enough time to debuf pet before charm again. The only real risks is when charm break at bad time like mem new spells, pull of multiple mobs or just as you cast a spell. I try never to keep the pet far away from me since I experience it agro on other group members if I get more then 10 feet away (can be used to save yourself too, better a death wizard is my motto <img src="images/smiles/icon_twisted.gif" alt="icon_twisted.gif" border="0" /> ). A second healer is a must because one healer is to high a risk or need extremly good skill.
<br />

<br />
Pooka's are really easy to charm compare to other places since mr are low and charm often last max duration. With the hp that the poster has I would not take to many risks in charm tho.
<br />

<br />
Sandyar</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
